-- KPI-Based Supplier Performance Evaluation

\\\On-Time Delivery Rate (OTD)
Purpose

Measures supplier delivery reliability.

Formula
On-Time Delivery Rate (%) =
(Number of On-Time Deliveries / Total Deliveries) × 100
SQL Logic
SUM(CASE WHEN is_on_time = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
/
COUNT(delivery_id)
* 100
Tables Used
deliveries

\\\Defect Rate
Purpose

Measures supplier quality performance.

Formula
Defect Rate (%) =
(Total Defective Items / Total Inspected Items) × 100
SQL Logic
SUM(defective_items)
/
SUM(total_items)
* 100
Tables Used
quality_inspections

\\\Fill Rate (Order Fulfillment Rate)
Purpose

Measures how completely suppliers fulfill orders.

Formula
Fill Rate (%) =
(Total Received Quantity / Total Ordered Quantity) × 100
SQL Logic
SUM(deliveries.received_quantity)
/
SUM(order_items.quantity)
* 100
Tables Used
deliveries
order_items

\\\Average Lead Time
Purpose

Measures supplier responsiveness speed.

Formula
Average Lead Time =
Average(actual_delivery_date - order_date)

Measured in:

days
SQL Logic
AVG(actual_delivery_date - order_date)
Tables Used
purchase_orders

\\\Inspection Pass Rate
Purpose

Measures percentage of deliveries passing inspection.

Formula
Inspection Pass Rate (%) =
(Number of Passed Inspections / Total Inspections) × 100
SQL Logic
SUM(CASE WHEN passed = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
/
COUNT(inspection_id)
* 100
Tables Used
quality_inspections

\\\Order Completion Rate
Purpose

Measures successful order completion.

Formula
Order Completion Rate (%) =
(Number of Completed Orders / Total Orders) × 100
SQL Logic
SUM(CASE WHEN order_status = 'completed' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
/
COUNT(order_id)
* 100
Tables Used
purchase_orders

\\\Overall Supplier Performance Score
Purpose

Combines all KPIs into one supplier evaluation score.

Formula

weighted model:

Overall Score =
(OTD × 0.30)
+
((100 - Defect Rate) × 0.30)
+
(Fill Rate × 0.20)
+
(Inspection Pass Rate × 0.20)
